>\r\n\t\t\t\t<span class=\"player_song_name transition3\" data-albumname=\"\">\r\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<\/span>\r\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<\/span>\r\n\r\n\t\t\t<span class=\"entry_duration mpfe_fix_lh\"><\/span>\t\t\r\n\r\n\t\t\t<span class=\"song_buy_icons compact_buy_icons transition3 clearfix mobile_visibility_hide\">\r\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<\/span>\r\n\r\n\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\r\n\r\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\r\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\r\n\t\t\t<\/div>\r\n\t\t<\/div>\r\n\r\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-1096906 all-sections-heading elementor-widget elementor-widget-heading\" data-id=\"1096906\" data-element_type=\"widget\" id=\"section-1\" data-settings=\"{&quot;ekit_we_effect_on&quot;:&quot;none&quot;}\" data-widget_type=\"heading.default\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-container\">\n\t\t\t\t\t<h2 class=\"elementor-heading-title elementor-size-default\">Introduction Why ServiceNow Still Wins<\/h2>\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-ea18eed elementor-widget elementor-widget-text-editor\" data-id=\"ea18eed\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-settings=\"{&quot;ekit_we_effect_on&quot;:&quot;none&quot;}\" data-widget_type=\"text-editor.default\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-container\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<p>Customers remember how you solve their issues long after they forget what you sold them. Yet legacy ticketing tools, siloed data, and manual hand-offs make \u201cgreat service\u201d feel impossible.<\/p><p>Enter ServiceNow Customer Service Management (CSM), a single-platform approach that unifies channels, automates <a href=\"https:\/\/www.servicenow.com\/workflows\/customer-workflows.html\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">ServiceNow CSM workflows<\/a>, and gives agents the context they need to wow customers at scale.<\/p><p>This guide explains what CSM is, how its omnichannel support in ServiceNow works, and the practical ServiceNow CSM implementation steps you need \u2013 whether you\u2019re a global enterprise or a fast-growing startup.<\/p><p><strong>Key Takeaways:<\/strong><\/p><ul><li>ServiceNow CSM workflows centralize requests, knowledge, and automation so agents resolve cases faster.<\/li><li>Out-of-the-box flows plus omnichannel support in ServiceNow (phone, chat, messaging, portals) meet customers wherever they are.<\/li><li>ServiceNow customer experience analytics surface trends and bottlenecks in real time, driving continuous improvement.<\/li><li>A phased implementation roadmap \u2013 from discovery to go-live \u2013 reduces risk and accelerates ROI.<\/li><li>CSM integration with CRM (e.g., Salesforce, Dynamics) creates a 360\u00b0 view without duplicate entry.<\/li><li>Purpose-built editions make ServiceNow CSM for small businesses affordable and fast to deploy.<\/li><\/ul>\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-bffafec all-sections-heading elementor-widget elementor-widget-heading\" data-id=\"bffafec\" data-element_type=\"widget\" id=\"section-2\" data-settings=\"{&quot;ekit_we_effect_on&quot;:&quot;none&quot;}\" data-widget_type=\"heading.default\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-container\">\n\t\t\t\t\t<h2 class=\"elementor-heading-title elementor-size-default\">What Is ServiceNow Customer Service Management?<\/h2>\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-d58ff45 elementor-widget elementor-widget-text-editor\" data-id=\"d58ff45\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-settings=\"{&quot;ekit_we_effect_on&quot;:&quot;none&quot;}\" data-widget_type=\"text-editor.default\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-container\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<p><a href=\"https:\/\/mountainise.com\/servicenow\/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">ServiceNow CSM<\/a> extends the Now Platform beyond IT tickets to every external customer request. Think of it as:<\/p><ul><li><strong>A digital front door<\/strong> \u2013 self-service portals, knowledge bases, and virtual agents handle routine questions 24\/7.<\/li><li><strong>An intelligent routing engine<\/strong> \u2013 cases auto-land with the right team, priority, and SLA.<\/li><li><strong>A workflow powerhouse<\/strong> \u2013 cross-department tasks (e.g., refunds or field-service dispatch) kick off the moment a case is logged.<\/li><li><strong>A data hub<\/strong> \u2013 native ServiceNow customer experience analytics track CSAT, first-contact resolution, backlog, and more in real time.<\/li><\/ul><p>Bottom line: CSM turns reactive contact centers into proactive experience hubs.<\/p>\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-0915a58 all-sections-heading elementor-widget elementor-widget-heading\" data-id=\"0915a58\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-settings=\"{&quot;ekit_we_effect_on&quot;:&quot;none&quot;}\" data-widget_type=\"heading.default\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-container\">\n\t\t\t\t\t<h2 class=\"elementor-heading-title elementor-size-default\">Who Should Use ServiceNow CSM?<\/h2>\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-4e5f08b elementor-widget elementor-widget-text-editor\" data-id=\"4e5f08b\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-settings=\"{&quot;ekit_we_effect_on&quot;:&quot;none&quot;}\" data-widget_type=\"text-editor.default\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-container\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Whether you&#8217;re managing a growing eCommerce store, a B2B SaaS business, or an enterprise helpdesk, ServiceNow CSM adapts to your support structure. If your team struggles with slow case resolution, duplicate tasks, or disconnected systems, CSM gives you one centralized platform to automate and scale your customer service efficiently.<\/span><\/p>\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-f0b3f75 all-sections-heading elementor-widget elementor-widget-heading\" data-id=\"f0b3f75\" data-element_type=\"widget\" id=\"section-3\" data-settings=\"{&quot;ekit_we_effect_on&quot;:&quot;none&quot;}\" data-widget_type=\"heading.default\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-container\">\n\t\t\t\t\t<h2 class=\"elementor-heading-title elementor-size-default\">Core ServiceNow CSM Workflows That Boost Productivity<\/h2>\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-d770a4e elementor-widget elementor-widget-text-editor\" data-id=\"d770a4e\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-settings=\"{&quot;ekit_we_effect_on&quot;:&quot;none&quot;}\" data-widget_type=\"text-editor.default\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-container\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<table><tbody><tr><td><p><b>Workflow<\/b><\/p><\/td><td><p><b>What It Does<\/b><\/p><\/td><td><p><b>Keyword Call-Out<\/b><\/p><\/td><\/tr><tr><td><p><b>Case &amp; Major-Issue Management<\/b><\/p><\/td><td><p><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Auto-assign, escalate, swarm; playbooks ensure consistency.<\/span><\/p><\/td><td><p><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">ServiceNow CSM workflows<\/span><\/p><\/td><\/tr><tr><td><p><b>Omnichannel Service<\/b><\/p><\/td><td><p><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Requests via web, chat, email, SMS, socials \u2013 all funnel into one agent view.<\/span><\/p><\/td><td><p><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Omnichannel support in ServiceNow<\/span><\/p><\/td><\/tr><tr><td><p><b>Knowledge-Centered Support<\/b><\/p><\/td><td><p><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">AI suggests articles to agents &amp; customers, deflecting repetitive questions.<\/span><\/p><\/td><td><p><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\"> \u2013\u00a0<\/span><\/p><\/td><\/tr><tr><td><p><b>Field-Service Integration<\/b><\/p><\/td><td><p><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Automatically creates work orders when on-site help is needed.<\/span><\/p><\/td><td><p><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\"> \u2013\u00a0<\/span><\/p><\/td><\/tr><tr><td><p><b>Proactive Service<\/b><\/p><\/td><td><p><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">IoT \/ monitoring triggers cases before customers notice an issue.<\/span><\/p><\/td><td><p><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\"> \u2013\u00a0<\/span><\/p><\/td><\/tr><\/tbody><\/table>\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-c366a55 all-sections-heading elementor-widget elementor-widget-heading\" data-id=\"c366a55\" data-element_type=\"widget\" id=\"section-4\" data-settings=\"{&quot;ekit_we_effect_on&quot;:&quot;none&quot;}\" data-widget_type=\"heading.default\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-container\">\n\t\t\t\t\t<h2 class=\"elementor-heading-title elementor-size-default\">Omnichannel Support in ServiceNow: Meeting Customers Where They Click<\/h2>\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-d45fd81 elementor-widget elementor-widget-text-editor\" data-id=\"d45fd81\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-settings=\"{&quot;ekit_we_effect_on&quot;:&quot;none&quot;}\" data-widget_type=\"text-editor.default\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-container\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<p>Modern users expect help in seconds, not hours. CSM\u2019s omnichannel layer provides:<\/p><ul><li><strong>Chat &amp; Messaging:<\/strong> Widgets for web, mobile, WhatsApp, Facebook, or SMS.<\/li><li><strong>Voice:<\/strong> Soft-phone integration pipes calls (plus transcripts) into the agent workspace.<\/li><li><strong>Self-Service Portals:<\/strong> Branded sites for case creation, tracking, and article browsing.<\/li><li><strong>Virtual Agent:<\/strong> Conversational AI resolves common tasks (password resets, order status).<\/li><\/ul><p>Agents see every interaction thread in one timeline, eliminating repeats of \u201cTell me your issue\u2026again.\u201d<\/p>\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-3d08ee1 elementor-widget elementor-widget-image\" data-id=\"3d08ee1\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-settings=\"{&quot;ekit_we_effect_on&quot;:&quot;none&quot;}\" data-widget_type=\"image.default\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-container\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<img decoding=\"async\" src=\"https:\/\/mountainise.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/elementor\/thumbs\/Omnichannel-Support-in-ServiceNow-r56dplei9v7ryuizk8zs720uk4n90m476up96oy4a8.webp\" title=\"Omnichannel Support in ServiceNow\" alt=\"Omnichannel Support in ServiceNow\" loading=\"lazy\" \/>\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-adeed39 all-sections-heading elementor-widget elementor-widget-heading\" data-id=\"adeed39\" data-element_type=\"widget\" id=\"section-5\" data-settings=\"{&quot;ekit_we_effect_on&quot;:&quot;none&quot;}\" data-widget_type=\"heading.default\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-container\">\n\t\t\t\t\t<h2 class=\"elementor-heading-title elementor-size-default\">Turning Data Into Decisions: ServiceNow Customer Experience Analytics<\/h2>\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-39ee1e1 elementor-widget elementor-widget-text-editor\" data-id=\"39ee1e1\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-settings=\"{&quot;ekit_we_effect_on&quot;:&quot;none&quot;}\" data-widget_type=\"text-editor.default\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-container\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<p>ServiceNow Performance Analytics layers KPIs and predictive insight on top of raw case data:<\/p><table><tbody><tr><td><p><b>KPI<\/b><\/p><\/td><td><p><b>Why It Matters<\/b><\/p><\/td><\/tr><tr><td><p><b>First-Contact Resolution<\/b><\/p><\/td><td><p><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Strongly tied to CSAT and cost per ticket.<\/span><\/p><\/td><\/tr><tr><td><p><b>Time to Resolution by Channel<\/b><\/p><\/td><td><p><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Highlights channels that need automation or staffing tweaks.<\/span><\/p><\/td><\/tr><tr><td><p><b>Volume by Issue Type<\/b><\/p><\/td><td><p><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Guides article creation and product fixes.<\/span><\/p><\/td><\/tr><tr><td><p><b>Customer Effort Score (CES)<\/b><\/p><\/td><td><p><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Better churn predictor than NPS.<\/span><\/p><\/td><\/tr><\/tbody><\/table><p><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Real-time dashboards let leaders re-allocate resources before backlogs explode.<\/span><\/p>\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-cd4ab31 all-sections-heading elementor-widget elementor-widget-heading\" data-id=\"cd4ab31\" data-element_type=\"widget\" id=\"section-6\" data-settings=\"{&quot;ekit_we_effect_on&quot;:&quot;none&quot;}\" data-widget_type=\"heading.default\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-container\">\n\t\t\t\t\t<h2 class=\"elementor-heading-title elementor-size-default\">ServiceNow CSM Implementation Steps: From Vision to Go-Live<\/h2>\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-835473b elementor-widget elementor-widget-text-editor\" data-id=\"835473b\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-settings=\"{&quot;ekit_we_effect_on&quot;:&quot;none&quot;}\" data-widget_type=\"text-editor.default\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-container\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<table><tbody><tr><td><p><b>Phase<\/b><\/p><\/td><td><p><b>Activities<\/b><\/p><\/td><td><p><b>Pro Tip<\/b><\/p><\/td><\/tr><tr><td><p><b>1\u00a0 \u2013\u00a0 Discovery<\/b><\/p><\/td><td><p><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Stakeholder workshops; map current support processes; capture baseline KPIs.<\/span><\/p><\/td><td><p><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Prioritize high-volume pain points.<\/span><\/p><\/td><\/tr><tr><td><p><b>2\u00a0 \u2013\u00a0 Design<\/b><\/p><\/td><td><p><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Configure data model, SLAs, channels, and core <\/span><b>ServiceNow CSM workflows<\/b><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">.<\/span><\/p><\/td><td><p><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Keep it simple \u2013 avoid early over-customization.<\/span><\/p><\/td><\/tr><tr><td><p><b>3\u00a0 \u2013\u00a0 Build &amp; Integrate<\/b><\/p><\/td><td><p><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Install CSM apps; automate with Flow Designer; set up <\/span><b>CSM integration with CRM<\/b><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\"> and ERP.<\/span><\/p><\/td><td><p><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Use IntegrationHub spokes to accelerate.<\/span><\/p><\/td><\/tr><tr><td><p><b>4\u00a0 \u2013\u00a0 Test<\/b><\/p><\/td><td><p><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Unit, system, and UAT cycles with real cases.<\/span><\/p><\/td><td><p><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Include voice-of-customer feedback loops.<\/span><\/p><\/td><\/tr><tr><td><p><b>5\u00a0 \u2013\u00a0 Train &amp; Launch<\/b><\/p><\/td><td><p><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Role-based training; phased rollout by team or region.<\/span><\/p><\/td><td><p><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Pair quick-ref guides with sandbox practice.<\/span><\/p><\/td><\/tr><tr><td><p><b>6\u00a0 \u2013\u00a0 Optimize<\/b><\/p><\/td><td><p><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Review analytics at 30\/60\/90 days; tune knowledge gaps and SLAs.<\/span><\/p><\/td><td><p><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Form a CSM Center of Excellence.<\/span><\/p><\/td><\/tr><\/tbody><\/table>\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-be22c7d all-sections-heading elementor-widget elementor-widget-heading\" data-id=\"be22c7d\" data-element_type=\"widget\" id=\"section-7\" data-settings=\"{&quot;ekit_we_effect_on&quot;:&quot;none&quot;}\" data-widget_type=\"heading.default\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-container\">\n\t\t\t\t\t<h2 class=\"elementor-heading-title elementor-size-default\">CSM Integration With CRM: Why Context Is King<\/h2>\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-9aba603 elementor-widget elementor-widget-text-editor\" data-id=\"9aba603\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-settings=\"{&quot;ekit_we_effect_on&quot;:&quot;none&quot;}\" data-widget_type=\"text-editor.default\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-container\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<p>Great service demands context orders, contracts, marketing touches, billing. Common patterns:<\/p><ul><li><strong>Native Salesforce\/Dynamics connectors<\/strong> via REST\/GraphQL.<\/li><li><strong>Real-Time iPaaS hubs<\/strong> (MuleSoft, Boomi) for bidirectional sync of accounts &amp; contacts.<\/li><li><strong>Event-Driven updates:<\/strong> CRM changes publish to ServiceNow (and back) within seconds.<\/li><\/ul><p>Outcome: agents view the full customer journey in one workspace; sales reps see open cases before renewal calls.<\/p>\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-fc4438b all-sections-heading elementor-widget elementor-widget-heading\" data-id=\"fc4438b\" data-element_type=\"widget\" id=\"section-8\" data-settings=\"{&quot;ekit_we_effect_on&quot;:&quot;none&quot;}\" data-widget_type=\"heading.default\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-container\">\n\t\t\t\t\t<h2 class=\"elementor-heading-title elementor-size-default\">ServiceNow CSM for Small Businesses \u2013 Big Impact, Starter Budget<\/h2>\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-27f09f2 elementor-widget elementor-widget-text-editor\" data-id=\"27f09f2\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-settings=\"{&quot;ekit_we_effect_on&quot;:&quot;none&quot;}\" data-widget_type=\"text-editor.default\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-container\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<p>You don\u2019t need a 500-seat contact center to benefit. The CSM Starter bundle offers:<\/p><ul><li>Pre-configured templates for rapid go-live.<\/li><li>Consumption-based licensing \u2013 pay for the tickets you handle.<\/li><li>Low-code Workflow Editor so non-devs can tweak processes.<\/li><\/ul><p>Result: a five-person support desk can deliver Amazon-level experiences without enterprise overhead.<\/p>\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-5a175a2 all-sections-heading elementor-widget elementor-widget-heading\" data-id=\"5a175a2\" data-element_type=\"widget\" id=\"section-9\" data-settings=\"{&quot;ekit_we_effect_on&quot;:&quot;none&quot;}\" data-widget_type=\"heading.default\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-container\">\n\t\t\t\t\t<h2 class=\"elementor-heading-title elementor-size-default\">Best Practices for Long-Term Success<\/h2>\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-3f24496 elementor-widget elementor-widget-text-editor\" data-id=\"3f24496\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-settings=\"{&quot;ekit_we_effect_on&quot;:&quot;none&quot;}\" data-widget_type=\"text-editor.default\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-container\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<ol><li><strong>Design for Self-Service First<\/strong> \u2013 every new FAQ can deflect dozens of tickets.<\/li><li><strong>Automate the Trigger &#8211;<\/strong>\u00a0Not the Relationship \u2013 bots gather data; humans handle empathy.<\/li><li><strong>Align KPIs Across Teams<\/strong> \u2013 support, product, and sales share a customer-centric scorecard.<\/li><li><strong>Review Workflows Quarterly<\/strong> \u2013 business evolves; your ServiceNow CSM workflows should too.<\/li><li><strong>Celebrate Wins Loudly<\/strong> \u2013 share metrics (e.g., 20 % faster resolutions) to keep momentum and budget.<\/li><\/ol>\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-f1bb367 all-sections-heading elementor-widget elementor-widget-heading\" data-id=\"f1bb367\" data-element_type=\"widget\" id=\"section-10\" data-settings=\"{&quot;ekit_we_effect_on&quot;:&quot;none&quot;}\" data-widget_type=\"heading.default\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-container\">\n\t\t\t\t\t<h2 class=\"elementor-heading-title elementor-size-default\">Conclusion<\/h2>\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-3238535 elementor-widget elementor-widget-text-editor\" data-id=\"3238535\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-settings=\"{&quot;ekit_we_effect_on&quot;:&quot;none&quot;}\" data-widget_type=\"text-editor.default\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-container\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<p>In today\u2019s experience economy, service is the new sales. Implementing ServiceNow Customer Service Management turns chaotic queues into streamlined, data-driven workflows \u2013 delighting customers and freeing agents to focus on high-value conversations.<\/p><p>Whether you\u2019re modernizing a global contact center or rolling out ServiceNow CSM for small businesses, the platform delivers:<\/p><ul><li>Faster resolutions through automation<\/li><li>Seamless omnichannel support in ServiceNow<\/li><li>Actionable insights via ServiceNow customer experience analytics<\/li><\/ul><p>Ready to press go? <a href=\"https:\/\/mountainise.com\/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">Mountainise<\/a> has guided orgs of every size through each stage of ServiceNow CSM implementation steps \u2013 from vision to optimization. Contact us for a free readiness assessment and discover how effortless world-class support can be.<\/p>\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-column elementor-col-33 elementor-top-column elementor-element elementor-element-e090308\" data-id=\"e090308\" data-element_type=\"column\">\n\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-wrap elementor-element-populated\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<section class=\"elementor-section elementor-inner-section elementor-element elementor-element-a8c1d4f elementor-section-boxed elementor-section-height-default elementor-section-height-default\" data-id=\"a8c1d4f\" data-element_type=\"section\" data-settings=\"{&quot;sticky&quot;:&quot;top&quot;,&quot;sticky_on&quot;:[&quot;desktop&quot;],&quot;sticky_parent&quot;:&quot;yes&quot;,&quot;ekit_has_onepagescroll_dot&quot;:&quot;yes&quot;,&quot;sticky_offset&quot;:0,&quot;sticky_effects_offset&quot;:0,&quot;sticky_anchor_link_offset&quot;:0}\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-container elementor-column-gap-no\">\n\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-column elementor-col-100 elementor-inner-column elementor-element elementor-element-59cc1c2\" data-id=\"59cc1c2\" data-element_type=\"column\">\n\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-wrap elementor-element-populated\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-209347a elementor-widget elementor-widget-heading\" data-id=\"209347a\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-settings=\"{&quot;ekit_we_effect_on&quot;:&quot;none&quot;}\" data-widget_type=\"heading.default\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-container\">\n\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-heading-title elementor-size-default\">Latest Whitepaper<\/div>\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-baa9ed8 elementor-grid-1 elementor-grid-tablet-2 elementor-grid-mobile-1 elementor-posts--thumbnail-top elementor-posts__hover-gradient elementor-widget elementor-widget-posts\" data-id=\"baa9ed8\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-settings=\"{&quot;cards_columns&quot;:&quot;1&quot;,&quot;cards_row_gap&quot;:{&quot;unit&quot;:&quot;px&quot;,&quot;size&quot;:5,&quot;sizes&quot;:[]},&quot;cards_columns_tablet&quot;:&quot;2&quot;,&quot;cards_columns_mobile&quot;:&quot;1&quot;,&quot;cards_row_gap_tablet&quot;:{&quot;unit&quot;:&quot;px&quot;,&quot;size&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;sizes&quot;:[]},&quot;cards_row_gap_mobile&quot;:{&quot;unit&quot;:&quot;px&quot;,&quot;size&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;sizes&quot;:[]},&quot;ekit_we_effect_on&quot;:&quot;none&quot;}\" data-widget_type=\"posts.cards\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-container\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-posts-container elementor-posts elementor-posts--skin-cards elementor-grid\" role=\"list\">\n\t\t\t\t<article class=\"elementor-post elementor-grid-item post-22071 post type-post status-publish format-standard has-post-thumbnail category-white-papers\" role=\"listitem\">\n\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-post__card\">\n\t\t\t\t<a class=\"elementor-post__thumbnail__link\" href=\"https:\/\/mountainise.com\/white-papers\/ai-powered-operations-organizational-growth\/\" tabindex=\"-1\" ><div class=\"elementor-post__thumbnail\"><img alt=\"\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"2048\" height=\"1088\" src=\"https:\/\/mountainise.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/04\/Frame-42-1.png\" class=\"attachment-full size-full wp-image-22074\" alt=\"\" srcset=\"https:\/\/mountainise.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/04\/Frame-42-1.png 2048w, https:\/\/mountainise.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/04\/Frame-42-1-300x159.png 300w, https:\/\/mountainise.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/04\/Frame-42-1-1024x544.png 1024w, https:\/\/mountainise.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/04\/Frame-42-1-768x408.png 768w, https:\/\/mountainise.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/04\/Frame-42-1-1536x816.png 1536w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 2048px) 100vw, 2048px\" \/><\/div><\/a>\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-post__text\">\n\t\t\t\t<h3 class=\"elementor-post__title\">\n\t\t\t<a href=\"https:\/\/mountainise.com\/white-papers\/ai-powered-operations-organizational-growth\/\" >\n\t\t\t\tHow AI-Powered Operations Support the Growth of Any Organization\t\t\t<\/a>\n\t\t<\/h3>\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-post__excerpt\">\n\t\t\t<p>This white paper examines the impact of advanced technology-powered operations on organizational growth and efficiency. Its purpose is to offer a comprehensive review of modern operational systems that enhance decision-making, streamline workflows, and lower costs. <\/p>\n\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t\t<